^B@2^*BMM: ^*NIn summary:
With 6-9 and support for partner's suit you bid based on the Law of Total tricks. 
^cBid 2 with 3-card support (ignore the double).
^CBid 3 with 4-card support and less than a limit raise. 
^cBid 4 with 5-card support.

^BWith 10+ points: 
^CYou redouble with 2 or 3-card support.
^CYou should bid 2NT (Jordan 2NT) with 4-card support and limit raise or better.|
